00:09:59.529 --> 00:10:06.610
It was really face strengthening to see how despite a pandemic, despite unrest, despite

00:10:06.610 --> 00:10:14.860
the country being in a state of emergency, our spiritual food supply continued to flow.

00:10:14.860 --> 00:10:19.820
What a blessing for our Roma-speaking brothers and sisters.

